      <title>中国监管机构要求 Temu 所有者 PDD 修正退款政策</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/china-watchdog-orders-temu-owner-pdd-to-fix-refunds-policy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国最高市场监管机构传唤拼多多控股有限公司高管，责令该公司修改退款优先政策，针对越来越多商家认为损害其利润的做法。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/china-watchdog-orders-temu-owner-pdd-to-fix-refunds-policy</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Dec 2024 09:31:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>前软银创始人 Akshay Naheta 考虑出售其稳定币初创公司的股份</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/ex-softbank-rainmaker-akshay-naheta-eyes-stake-sale-in-his-stablecoin-startup</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，阿克沙伊·纳赫塔 (Akshay Naheta) 曾是软银集团公司的高管，以负责监督该公司的一些最大交易而闻名，他目前正在就出售其共同创立的稳定币支付初创公司的少数股权进行初步谈判。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/ex-softbank-rainmaker-akshay-naheta-eyes-stake-sale-in-his-stablecoin-startup</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Dec 2024 08:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Zalando 以 13 亿美元收购德国零售商 About You</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/zalando-to-buy-german-online-retailer-about-you-for-1-3-billion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国在线时尚零售商 Zalando SE 同意以约 12 亿欧元（13 亿美元）收购竞争对手 About You Holding SE，以期主导欧洲电子商务市场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/zalando-to-buy-german-online-retailer-about-you-for-1-3-billion</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Dec 2024 07:18:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>阿联酋金融科技公司从花旗银行获得 5 亿美元资产支持贷款</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/abu-dhabi-fintech-tees-up-500-million-line-of-credit-from-citi</link>
      <description><![CDATA[花旗集团向阿布扎比 Astra Tech 的一家子公司提供 5 亿美元融资，这是阿联酋金融科技公司获得的最大单笔融资之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/abu-dhabi-fintech-tees-up-500-million-line-of-credit-from-citi</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Dec 2024 07:15:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>据称 I Squared Capital 将开始对香港宽频进行尽职调查</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/i-squared-capital-is-said-to-begin-due-diligence-work-on-hkbn</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士称，美国私募股权公司 I Squared Capital 已开始对香港上市的香港宽频有限公司 (HKBN Ltd.) 进行尽职调查，这家公司准备对这家宽带公司发出正式收购要约。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/i-squared-capital-is-said-to-begin-due-diligence-work-on-hkbn</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Dec 2024 03:03:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亚通 (Axiata) 与金光集团 (Sinar Mas) 以 65 亿美元的交易合并印度尼西亚子公司</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/axiata-sinar-mas-to-merge-indonesian-units-in-6-5-billion-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[马来西亚无线运营商 Axiata Group Bhd. 和印尼企业集团 PT Sinar Mas Group 同意合并其在印尼的电信业务，交易价值为 65 亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/axiata-sinar-mas-to-merge-indonesian-units-in-6-5-billion-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Dec 2024 02:44:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>习近平为应对美国贸易战准备好筹码</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/xi-readies-bargaining-chips-for-us-trade-war-after-biden-curbs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[如果唐纳德·特朗普兑现其威胁，用关税惩罚世界第二大经济体，中国将展示其准备使用的一系列新工具，以便在与美国爆发贸易战时抢占先机。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/xi-readies-bargaining-chips-for-us-trade-war-after-biden-curbs</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Dec 2024 02:35:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>前格罗弗首席执行官计划重返公司，以结束可能的股权蒸发</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/ousted-ceo-plots-return-to-end-possible-equity-wipeout-at-grover</link>
      <description><![CDATA[陷入困境的设备租赁初创公司格罗弗 (Grover) 的创始人格罗弗 (Grover) 一年前被迫离开公司，目前正试图通过对抗可能抹去投资者股权价值的重组来东山再起。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/ousted-ceo-plots-return-to-end-possible-equity-wipeout-at-grover</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 20:16:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国网络安全公司受到美国制裁，员工遭指控</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/chinese-cybersecurity-firm-sanctioned-employee-charged-by-us</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国对一家中国公司实施制裁，指控其为情报机构工作，并指控其一名员工入侵全球数千家企业的计算机系统，其中包括美国关键基础设施公司。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/chinese-cybersecurity-firm-sanctioned-employee-charged-by-us</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 18:12:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>TikTok Shop 在欧洲上线西班牙和爱尔兰市场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/tiktok-shop-goes-live-for-spain-in-first-step-of-europe-rollout</link>
      <description><![CDATA[TikTok 的应用内购物功能已向西班牙和爱尔兰用户上线，这标志着字节跳动有限公司在欧洲增长最快的业务扩张的第一步。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/tiktok-shop-goes-live-for-spain-in-first-step-of-europe-rollout</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 09:44:57 GMT</pubDate>
